Source-Makefile: package/ssmtp/Makefile
Package: ssmtp
Version: 2.64-1.1
Depends: +libopenssl
Provides: 
Build-Depends: 
Section: mail
Category: Mail
Title: A minimal and secure mail sender with ssl support
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Type: ipkg
Description:  A secure, effective and simple way of getting mail off a system to your
 mail hub. It contains no suid-binaries or other dangerous things - no
 mail spool to poke around in, and no daemons running in the background.
 Mail is simply forwarded to the configured mailhost. Extremely easy
 configuration.

http://packages.debian.org/ssmtp
